        <scopecontent id="ref4">
            <head>Scope and Content Note</head>
            <p>This unprocessed collection contains conference and convention materials, correspondence, minutes, position papers, reports, educctional materials, commission, task force and chapter files, issues of NAM's discussion and internal bulletins, printed ephemera, some files on other socialist and left organizations, of which some contain discussion NAM's relations with these organizations, including discussion within NAM on whether or not to merge with the Democratic Socialist Organizing Committee to form the Democratic Socialists of America. NOTE: this collection is stored offsite and advance notice is required for its use.</p>
            <p>There is, for box 1, a folder level inventory, and for boxes 2-20, a box level inventory. In addition, at the Library, there is a more detailed handwritten inventory for boxes 2-19.</p>
            <p>PLEASE DIRECT FURTHER INQUIRIES TO: peter.filardo@nyu.edu</p>
